    <data key="d0">Infor Governance Risk and Compliance Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gNMEyei-co</data>
    <data key="d2">Ingests millions of transactions daily into Aurora and S3. Uses Fargate and EMR Spark to scope and execute rule audits, forwarding violations to EventBridge/SQS.</data>
